---
title: Cheesy Plant-Based Patty Melt 'Pockets' with Beyond Meat® and Garden Salad
description: Combine savoury and cheesy flavours of diner classic patty melts with beloved Italian street food, calzones and what you have is a meal mash-up the whole family will love. Served with a fresh salad, it's a recipe for an irresistible dinner!
